to help us out,
sounded real generous, too.

17:54.699 --> 17:56.951
Says he’s gonna fly
right down from New York.

17:57.035 --> 17:58.445
Well, I want to meet him.

17:59.996 --> 18:03.033
Oh, right, well,
I don't know about that.

18:03.667 --> 18:04.998
But he's my father.

18:05.293 --> 18:06.908
Right, well,

18:08.421 --> 18:11.208
why don't I talk to him,
and we'll see what he says?

18:11.883 --> 18:13.259
You know what, Claire,
I actually have to go,

18:13.343 --> 18:15.550
but I’ll call you later,
all right?

18:17.347 --> 18:18.336
I love you.

18:47.752 --> 18:51.040
MALSKY: I've got the money.
Let's see the diamonds.

18:52.841 --> 18:55.082
Stones range from
two to nine karats.

18:57.345 --> 18:59.301
My offer is
more than generous.

19:02.892 --> 19:07.556
DEALER: Not that it matters.
Linderman’s guy
will be here soon.

19:08.148 --> 19:10.230
You won’t get out alive.

19:13.320 --> 19:15.151
Sir, sir, please.

19:15.238 --> 19:16.978
We've got to get
out of here right now.

19:17.073 --> 19:18.688
This is a setup.

19:18.908 --> 19:19.988
What?
How do you know that?

19:20.076 --> 19:22.283
| just do.
You have to trust me.

19:27.959 --> 19:30.450
You've got a deal.
I gotta run.

19:38.261 --> 19:39.296
Who's Linderman?

19:39.387 --> 19:41.343
My ex-employer.
How do you know his name?

19:41.431 --> 19:42.420
Never mind.

19:42.515 --> 19:44.221
Why has he sent
someone here to kill you?

19:44.309 --> 19:46.425
Because I stole
his two million.

19:46.519 --> 19:48.305
/ should have been
out of the country by now.

19:48.396 --> 19:50.603
Oh, great.
You stole the money.

19:50.815 --> 19:52.066
How do you know?

19:54.611 --> 19:57.353
Please, you've gotta
get me out of here.

20:01.409 --> 20:04.116
Take this.
There's another one for you
when you get me out.

20:04.204 --> 20:05.535
No, no. You can't bribe me.

20:05.622 --> 20:06.782
I don't want to die.

20:06.956 --> 20:08.537
JESSICA: Two in the bodyguard.

20:08.625 --> 20:10.741
Then Malsky gets
one in the gut.

20:10.835 --> 20:14.748
Two in the bodyguard,
then Malsky gets
one in the gut.

20:19.052 --> 20:20.132
She's in there.

20:40.323 --> 20:41.824
This should be fun.

20:49.666 --> 20:53.375
HOPE: I do all the work.
He takes half the profit.
I'm sick of it.

20:53.461 --> 20:56.419
No, I got these two
Chinese guys to help me out.

20:56.506 --> 20:59.669
Turned on the waterworks,
and they were mine. Yep.

21:00.635 --> 21:03.377
