We are Japanese.

21:28.455 --> 21:29.695
Whatever.

21:31.332 --> 21:33.789
Where's the bag?

21:36.754 --> 21:38.710
You are bad person.

21:39.257 --> 21:42.374
You may fool Ando,
but you do not fool me.

21:42.719 --> 21:44.710
