21:44.846 --> 21:45.835
(GRUNTS)

21:46.806 --> 21:48.216
(MALSKY PANTING)

21:52.145 --> 21:53.601
(WHEEZING)

21:54.397 --> 21:56.729
What are you doing?
We can't stop here.

21:57.150 --> 21:58.481
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

22:02.447 --> 22:04.938
Back up. This way!
Come on! Come on!

22:06.826 --> 22:07.906
Go to the elevator.

22:17.921 --> 22:19.206
You can't do this.

22:23.176 --> 22:24.712
You have to stop!

